  "text": "This pathogenetic mechanism is similar to that of MorelLavallée lesions where, however, the virtual cavity that develops due to the traumatic event may also contain lymph and adipose tissues. Moreover, such lesions are rarely chronic and more frequently occur after a sports injury or motor vehicle accidents [CITATION_1] .",
